{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/fe/2018/07/07/GulpV4之后Task必须要传函数.html","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"宫不上叔"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"2c529101-cd54-5557-8ead-41253e6217f0","excerpt":"Gulp v4 之后 task 必须传函数 https://fettblog.eu/gulp-4-parallel-and-series/ 如链接所说，为实现并行操作，原来的 已经改为 而如果想串行执行的话可以用","html":"<h1>Gulp v4 之后 task 必须传函数</h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://fettblog.eu/gulp-4-parallel-and-series/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">https://fettblog.eu/gulp-4-parallel-and-series/</a></p>\n<p>如链接所说，为实现并行操作，原来的</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">gulp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">task</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"default\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"html\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"js\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>已经改为</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">gulp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">task</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"default\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> gulp<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">parallel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">\"css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"html\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"js\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>而如果想串行执行的话可以用<code class=\"language-text\">gulp.series</code></p>","frontmatter":{"category":"fe"},"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2018/07/07/GulpV4之后Task必须要传函数.html","date":"July 07, 2018","title":"GulpV4之后Task必须要传函数"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/fe/2018/07/07/GulpV4之后Task必须要传函数.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/plan/2018/07/05/补一下6月的总结.html","title":"补一下6月的总结"},"frontmatter":{"category":"plan"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2018/07/10/没有手动配置过Apollo都不知道Meteor帮你做了多少事.html","title":"没有手动配置过Apollo都不知道Meteor帮你做了多少事"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}}}}}